        "text": " (",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Jam 1:5",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "), is not intended to be indicated, that the fault of not being heard lies not with God but with man; rather he receives not, because God gives not.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
